1
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:00,000
The Story of Ming Lan

2
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,959
Episode 16

3
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,480
Second Brother Gu is here.

4
00:01:46,279 --> 00:01:47,480
The one next to him is Chief Wei.

5
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:50,639
Miss Yun from Qiyun House is here too.

6
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:53,959
Second Uncle Gu?

7
00:01:53,959 --> 00:01:55,000
You're getting the generations

8
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,879
all mixed up.

9
00:01:56,599 --> 00:01:57,400
Second Brother Gu.

10
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,080
Look at my foolish older brother.

11
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:02,680
He can't even

12
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,480
behave with dignity.

13
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:05,239
Seeing how Qiu House is

14
00:02:05,239 --> 00:02:06,319
getting abandoned by His Majesty,

15
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:08,039
he starts to curry favor with Gu House right away.

16
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:10,119
That little scheme of his.

17
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,119
Everyone can tell it.

18
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,160
Shameful.

19
00:02:27,679 --> 00:02:28,880
Your second brother, Changbai

20
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:30,559
is so busy at Imperial Hanlin Academy.

21
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:34,080
But he's got the leisure

22
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,759
to go see the chief of a brothel.

23
00:02:36,839 --> 00:02:38,279
Let him go, Mother.

24
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:41,800
Mother, I want to play Chui Wan.

25
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:44,759
Go then.

26
00:02:55,119 --> 00:02:56,039
Big Madam,

27
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,199
Yanran is over there.

28
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:01,520
Go then.

29
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,759
It's not easy

30
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:03,639
to come out to have fun.

31
00:03:11,279 --> 00:03:12,479
Madam Wang,

32
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:15,039
I have been waiting for you for a long time.

33
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:17,320
I arranged a seat for you.

34
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:17,720
Come with me.

35
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,279
Yanran.

36
00:03:33,199 --> 00:03:33,960
Minglan.

37
00:03:39,759 --> 00:03:40,800
You are here too.

38
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,399
Your “hundred birds looking at wind” embroidery,

39
00:03:42,399 --> 00:03:43,800
I'm almost done getting it mounted for you.

40
00:03:44,679 --> 00:03:46,800
But your thread wasn't great this time,

41
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,679
it almost blotched.

42
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,360
Blotched?

43
00:03:50,199 --> 00:03:51,039
What should I do?

44
00:03:51,039 --> 00:03:52,080
Then it can't be gifted out,

45
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,039
my step-mother will have words for me

46
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:53,839
for sure again.

47
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,759
Don't worry,

48
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:56,600
I added fish gelatin to it

49
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,600
and preserved the color,

50
00:03:58,559 --> 00:04:01,199
but now the

51
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:03,320
prop method won't work,

52
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,320
and the wood board is heavy.

53
00:04:04,559 --> 00:04:06,639
I want to try the pad method.

54
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,639
I'm pretty sure it will work.

55
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:09,520
Tomorrow, I'll be sure to deliver

56
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,039
two bottles of Cuoren wine.

57
00:04:21,559 --> 00:04:23,160
Why isn't Brother Yuanruo here yet?

58
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:25,440
Didn't he say

59
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,480
he would be here?

60
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:29,359
Miss, look.

61
00:04:29,359 --> 00:04:30,959
Rong House's Miss Feiyan is here too,

62
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:33,040
so that Young Lord must be here.

63
00:04:34,239 --> 00:04:36,119
Princess Jiacheng and Rong Feiyan

64
00:04:36,119 --> 00:04:37,000
are already here.

65
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,399
Brother Yuanruo will naturally be here too.

66
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:42,239
I think the

67
00:04:42,239 --> 00:04:43,480
thread from Li House is the best,

68
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,720
but it's expensive,

69
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:47,119
so I thought the shop under the bridge would do.

70
00:04:47,119 --> 00:04:48,239
I didn't realize.

71
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,839
You are not allowed to hit it.

72
00:04:49,839 --> 00:04:50,920
That ball is mine!

73
00:05:00,679 --> 00:05:01,839
Your Second Brother

74
00:05:01,839 --> 00:05:02,440
and Third Sister are here too.

75
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,040
They're here.

76
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,559
Princess Jiacheng from Prince Yong's house

77
00:05:05,559 --> 00:05:06,160
is here too.

78
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:08,200
My Third Sister will come for sure.

79
00:05:09,839 --> 00:05:11,600
Miss Rong,

80
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,160
I'm very happy that you are here.

81
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,119
Madam Wu.

82
00:05:15,119 --> 00:05:17,000
Quick, come in and take a seat.

83
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:02,959
This way, please.

84
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,000
Young Lord, make a poem.

85
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:09,320
Yes, Young Lord, make a poem.

86
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,679
Make a poem. Yes, a poem!

87
00:06:13,119 --> 00:06:14,839
Brother Qi.

88
00:06:14,839 --> 00:06:16,279
”The bee's waist faces the butterfly's wing.

89
00:06:16,679 --> 00:06:18,600
Hangover faces residual sobriety”.

90
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:21,119
That last word rhymes with your name of Heng.

91
00:06:21,119 --> 00:06:21,839
So let's use that as the final rhyme

92
00:06:21,839 --> 00:06:23,079
on eight-syllable stanzas.

93
00:06:23,359 --> 00:06:24,559
You make a good poem,

94
00:06:24,559 --> 00:06:26,119
and I'll let you take this stew.

95
00:06:31,279 --> 00:06:33,799
Alright. For this fish stew,

96
00:06:33,799 --> 00:06:35,160
I must make a poem then.

97
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:55,200
The willow leaves are like bright blades.

98
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:59,559
The lead is half-gone.

99
00:07:01,839 --> 00:07:05,359
At the pavilion for a gathering today.

100
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:09,399
Then departing after today until next time.

101
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,440
Excellent.

102
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,799
Brother Yuanruo's poem is excellent.

103
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:24,239
Spring breeze as sharp as a knife.

104
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,200
As sharp as a willow leaf.

105
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,839
Tender grass both yellow and green.

106
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:31,040
Akin to a young maiden's mirror on the dressing table.

107
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,640
Her eyebrows bent like the willow leaf.

108
00:07:33,679 --> 00:07:36,559
But upon meeting today,

109
00:07:36,559 --> 00:07:37,640
never meeting again.

110
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,799
That's a pun in each line.

111
00:07:43,679 --> 00:07:44,640
You praise me, Fourth Miss.

112
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:48,119
Brother Yuanruo, your poem is beautiful,

113
00:07:48,119 --> 00:07:49,880
but it feels sad.

114
00:07:50,839 --> 00:07:52,839
How about changing it to…

115
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:55,160
"brush bestowed upon a lilac town"?

116
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,600
Does it sound more lively?

117
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:58,480
Great, love the lilac town.

118
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:00,720
Young Lord, when did you ever meet

119
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,320
such a clever miss?

120
00:08:03,519 --> 00:08:05,200
This is Jiying Alley's

121
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:06,279
Minister Sheng's Fourth Daughter.

122
00:08:09,839 --> 00:08:10,679
You met them

123
00:08:10,679 --> 00:08:11,959
in the past.

124
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:16,600
I remember now.

125
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,399
It was when I visited

126
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:18,440
the Sheng family with my mother.

127
00:08:19,119 --> 00:08:20,040
The Miss

128
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,559
who was startled by the screen.

129
00:08:23,119 --> 00:08:24,440
Greetings, Sixth Young Master Liang.

130
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:27,359
That day, my younger sister was reckless

131
00:08:27,359 --> 00:08:28,399
and we offended you.

132
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:30,679
No matter.

133
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:33,840
But the ‘cheng' in half undone,

134
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,919
and ‘cheng' in lilac town are repeats.

135
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,520
This poem is ruined by it.

136
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:38,960
Yes, it's repeated.

137
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,039
Go, go.

138
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:41,479
You've not finished reading half a book,

139
00:08:41,479 --> 00:08:42,200
so what do you know?

140
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:43,880
This Miss Sheng's grandfather

141
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:44,599
placed third in the Hanlin Exam.

142
00:08:44,599 --> 00:08:45,599
They are the original scholars.

143
00:08:47,719 --> 00:08:49,080
Fourth Miss Sheng,

144
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,640
this outdoor fair my mother put together

145
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,599
has everything.

146
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,760
There are polo, Chui Wan, fishing and hunting.

147
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,000
I wonder

148
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,960
what you like.

149
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:02,479
How is Imperial Tutor lately?

150
00:09:03,559 --> 00:09:05,080
Grandfather is doing well.

151
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,000
It's just that he and Grandmother

152
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,239
are worried about my marriage.

153
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,880
After I have a prospect,

154
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:10,960
I think

155
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:11,919
they will retire to their hometown.

156
00:09:13,119 --> 00:09:14,679
Minglan, at that time,

157
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:15,559
in Bianjing,

158
00:09:16,159 --> 00:09:17,559
you'll be the only one left for me.

159
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:20,479
What are you afraid of?

160
00:09:21,599 --> 00:09:23,400
If you can be your own boss,

161
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,520
that's better than anything.

162
00:09:26,479 --> 00:09:27,840
Later on,

163
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:30,159
if Imperial Tutor Yu

164
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:31,359
really goes to Xuzhou,

165
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:32,679
then come to me.

166
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,960
I won!

167
00:09:41,599 --> 00:09:44,359
Being motherless is like being fatherless too.

168
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:46,559
I really don't know

169
00:09:46,559 --> 00:09:47,880
how I will manage to live.

170
00:09:51,799 --> 00:09:53,520
You and I both don't have our mothers anymore,

171
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:55,119
but we still

172
00:09:55,119 --> 00:09:56,200
have grandparents who protect us.

173
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:57,559
What's there to be scared of?

174
00:09:57,559 --> 00:09:59,159
We don't lack at all.

175
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:00,840
No matter what anyone says,

176
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,880
you're the legitimate-line eldest daughter

177
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:02,840
of Imperial Tutor Yu.

178
00:10:03,719 --> 00:10:05,080
You're much better off than so many.

179
00:10:05,719 --> 00:10:07,320
Hurry now. Straighten your back.

180
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,960
Third Miss of Yu House wins the match.

181
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:17,159
The prize is awarded, a white jade bracelet!

182
00:10:34,159 --> 00:10:34,799
Little Sister.

183
00:10:34,799 --> 00:10:35,359
Second Brother!

184
00:10:35,359 --> 00:10:36,320
Congratulations.

185
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,000
Thank you.

186
00:10:42,239 --> 00:10:42,719
Rest up.

187
00:10:42,719 --> 00:10:44,239
A new match.

188
00:10:45,039 --> 00:10:46,719
This match's prize

189
00:10:46,719 --> 00:10:50,119
is a gold pin with silk twists.

190
00:10:55,719 --> 00:10:56,559
Look,

191
00:10:56,559 --> 00:10:57,280
how pretty is that gold silk!

192
00:10:57,599 --> 00:10:59,039
I want that gold pin, Second Brother.

193
00:10:59,039 --> 00:10:59,760
You help me!

194
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,280
Miss.

195
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:19,520
Miss?

196
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:31,000
What's wrong?

197
00:11:32,799 --> 00:11:34,719
It's my late mother's item.

198
00:11:35,239 --> 00:11:36,359
What?

199
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:41,479
That's my mother's dowry for me.

200
00:11:41,919 --> 00:11:43,479
My name is engraved on it.

201
00:11:44,159 --> 00:11:45,880
I lost it a few years ago,

202
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:47,760
and haven't been able to find it.

203
00:11:48,039 --> 00:11:49,440
How could it be?

204
00:11:51,919 --> 00:11:52,840
When I went on tour

205
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:53,919
with Father a few years ago,

206
00:11:54,799 --> 00:11:56,640
things would go missing from my room often.

207
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,400
I asked, but couldn't find out anything.

208
00:11:58,400 --> 00:11:59,559
I didn't manage it and investigate it either.

209
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,400
I don't have more than one or two accessories

210
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:03,440
left from Mother.

211
00:12:04,599 --> 00:12:05,679
Minglan.

212
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:06,719
That pin.

213
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,320
I must get it today.

214
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:11,200
Didn't you just get a bracelet?

215
00:12:11,479 --> 00:12:12,320
A bracelet is a bracelet,

216
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,280
and a pin is a pin.

217
00:12:13,719 --> 00:12:14,919
I just want this gold pin.

218
00:12:16,760 --> 00:12:18,640
Not going to help me?

219
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:19,359
I?

220
00:12:19,359 --> 00:12:21,400
Fine. Don't want to help me?

221
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:22,719
When I go back, I will tell Grandfather.

222
00:12:22,919 --> 00:12:24,000
I will tell him that

223
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,159
you are not going to

224
00:12:25,159 --> 00:12:26,679
the Poetry Society tonight

225
00:12:26,679 --> 00:12:28,200
and that you're secretly going to sleep over

226
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,039
at Wide Cloud Terrace.

227
00:12:29,239 --> 00:12:30,280
Please don't.

228
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:31,520
I agree, okay?

229
00:12:31,559 --> 00:12:32,799
The competition is beginning.

230
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,599
That's

231
00:12:33,599 --> 00:12:34,280
what you said.

232
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:35,239
Thank you, Second Brother.

233
00:12:37,359 --> 00:12:38,719
But the teams are a man and a woman.

234
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,000
Your Second Brother and Third Sister

235
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,239
will definitely be in the same team.

236
00:12:41,679 --> 00:12:43,200
Who will you play with?

237
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,039
I…

238
00:12:46,359 --> 00:12:47,559
Where's your Third Brother?

239
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:51,640
Third Brother!

240
00:12:52,719 --> 00:12:53,640
Wait for me.

241
00:12:56,799 --> 00:12:58,000
Third Brother.

242
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:02,080
Third Brother. Hello, Second Uncle.

243
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:02,799
I need your help

244
00:13:02,799 --> 00:13:04,119
urgently.

245
00:13:04,119 --> 00:13:05,239
What is it? I…

246
00:13:05,479 --> 00:13:06,479
See you later.

247
00:13:12,119 --> 00:13:13,119
What are you doing?

248
00:13:13,119 --> 00:13:14,760
I was talking to Second Brother Gu.

249
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,039
Do a favor for Yanran.

250
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,239
What favor?

251
00:13:18,359 --> 00:13:19,919
Team up with her to play polo.

252
00:13:20,359 --> 00:13:21,479
I haven't played polo for a long time.

253
00:13:21,479 --> 00:13:22,119
I can't do it.

254
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:23,479
Go now. You can do it.

255
00:13:24,119 --> 00:13:25,599
Who's that lady?

256
00:13:25,599 --> 00:13:27,119
Why is she crying so miserably?

257
00:13:30,919 --> 00:13:32,119
The eldest daughter of the Yu family.

258
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,159
Eldest daughter of the Yu family?

259
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:38,320
Did you recognize the wrong person?

260
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:41,520
I am acquainted with the second son of Yu House.

261
00:13:42,039 --> 00:13:44,239
I only heard of him having a younger sister

262
00:13:44,239 --> 00:13:45,440
who is the third daughter.

263
00:13:47,719 --> 00:13:49,159
Darling Second, you may not know.

264
00:13:49,880 --> 00:13:52,000
The eldest daughter was born

265
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,440
to the first main wife of the Fan family.

266
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:55,880
But later on Madam Fan passed away,

267
00:13:55,880 --> 00:13:57,679
and Lord Yu remarried.

268
00:13:58,239 --> 00:14:00,039
Second Young Master Yu and Third Miss Yu

269
00:14:00,039 --> 00:14:01,159
were born to

270
00:14:01,159 --> 00:14:02,080
the new Madam.

271
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:08,039
The step-wife has control of Yu House.

272
00:14:08,559 --> 00:14:09,159
This Miss naturally

273
00:14:09,159 --> 00:14:10,599
became superfluous

274
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,200
and she was raised by the grandfather,

275
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:12,799
Imperial Tutor Yu.

276
00:14:14,599 --> 00:14:15,679
Eldest Miss Yu has the most amiable

277
00:14:15,679 --> 00:14:18,000
and refined disposition.

278
00:14:18,359 --> 00:14:19,799
No matter who seeks knowledge from her,

279
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,200
she is willing to help.

280
00:14:21,640 --> 00:14:22,919
Even people like us

281
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:23,919
who set up a meeting to invite her,

282
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:25,880
she's never declined us.

283
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:31,880
Even when you invite her,

284
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:33,119
she doesn't decline?

285
