00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:48,239
because her mother is pampered,

573
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,719
she pushed the eldest legitimate daughter out

574
00:33:49,719 --> 00:33:50,359
with no place to stand.

575
00:33:51,119 --> 00:33:51,959
She was born to a mother

576
00:33:51,959 --> 00:33:53,160
who's the step-wife after marriage.

577
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:53,959
What justification does she have

578
00:33:53,959 --> 00:33:55,119
to trample on the first wife's

579
00:33:55,119 --> 00:33:56,079
legitimate eldest daughter?

580
00:33:56,479 --> 00:33:58,079
She needs a good lesson.

581
00:33:58,359 --> 00:33:59,880
Miss,

582
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:01,199
your rosewood hare brush.

583
00:34:02,239 --> 00:34:03,839
Sixth Miss has one too.

584
00:34:05,520 --> 00:34:06,599
How can she have one too?

585
00:34:06,760 --> 00:34:07,959
Aren't there only two?

586
00:34:08,120 --> 00:34:09,080
One was given to Rulan,

587
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:09,879
and one to me.

588
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:12,879
Sixth Miss put it in an inconspicuous place

589
00:34:12,879 --> 00:34:14,040
in the drawer.

590
00:34:14,479 --> 00:34:15,760
Mei'er saw it after

591
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:16,520
her second time in the room.

592
00:34:16,840 --> 00:34:18,879
As soon as she saw it,

593
00:34:18,879 --> 00:34:19,760
she was chased out

594
00:34:19,760 --> 00:34:20,560
by Sister Danju.

595
00:34:21,560 --> 00:34:22,560
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

596
00:34:24,399 --> 00:34:25,879
I thought

597
00:34:25,879 --> 00:34:27,520
you already had one.

598
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:28,439
Is that the same?

599
00:34:29,439 --> 00:34:31,159
That means Brother Yuanruo

600
00:34:31,159 --> 00:34:32,520
gave her a total of three

601
00:34:32,879 --> 00:34:34,000
while he gave me none!

602
00:34:37,239 --> 00:34:38,239
Silly girl.

603
00:34:38,239 --> 00:34:40,159
I'm asking you about the Young Lord.

604
00:34:40,159 --> 00:34:41,760
I'm talking about him too.

605
00:34:42,679 --> 00:34:44,120
As long as he doesn't talk to Molan

606
00:34:44,120 --> 00:34:45,639
and she's angry, I will be happy.

607
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:48,639
Mother, look. Molan is so furious

608
00:34:48,639 --> 00:34:50,600
that she threw her fan away!

609
00:34:53,239 --> 00:34:55,159
Miss, Young Master Liang

610
00:34:55,159 --> 00:34:56,600
is looking this way.

611
00:34:57,479 --> 00:35:00,199
Wicked girl. She's sneaking behind my back!

612
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:20,800
Mother.

613
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:22,080
Keep your eye on the ball.

614
00:35:22,080 --> 00:35:23,320
Stop looking around wildly.

615
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:24,479
Yes.

616
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:31,840
She's pretending to smile at me now.

617
00:35:34,199 --> 00:35:35,000
Look!

618
00:35:59,159 --> 00:36:00,679
Only half an incense stick of time left.

619
00:36:00,679 --> 00:36:02,040
Let them fight it.

620
00:36:02,239 --> 00:36:04,080
That hairpin is just average

621
00:36:04,120 --> 00:36:05,439
so why so competitive?

622
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:28,120
Expert Second Master,

623
00:36:28,159 --> 00:36:29,399
you don't need to be so desperate.

624
00:36:29,399 --> 00:36:30,280
I don't have a choice.

625
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:33,040
Third Miss,

626
00:36:33,040 --> 00:36:34,159
we're playing a civilized game.

627
00:36:34,199 --> 00:36:34,959
What do you mean by this?

628
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:36,479
I can play however I like.

629
00:36:36,479 --> 00:36:37,520
Why do you care?

630
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:38,320
You mean,

631
00:36:38,320 --> 00:36:39,399
we're playing a martial game?

632
00:36:39,479 --> 00:36:40,959
Yes, a martial match!

633
00:36:51,879 --> 00:36:54,479
Young Lord, what are you doing?

634
00:36:54,840 --> 00:36:55,760
He can do

635
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:56,719
whatever he likes.

636
00:36:56,719 --> 00:36:57,600
Why do you care?

637
00:36:57,600 --> 00:36:58,479
You!

638
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:32,080
If I had known earlier, I would have played!

639
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:50,520
The incense stick is extinguished.

640
00:37:50,520 --> 00:37:52,000
Yellow team, seven points.

641
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:55,639
Yellow team wins!

642
00:38:03,360 --> 00:38:04,120
Minglan.

643
00:38:10,679 --> 00:38:11,360
Minglan.

644
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:16,120
This pin.

645
00:38:16,120 --> 00:38:17,560
Though it's Miss Yu's item

646
00:38:17,800 --> 00:38:18,840
in my heart

647
00:38:18,840 --> 00:38:19,919
I only regard it as doing it for you.

648
00:38:21,639 --> 00:38:22,199
I played

649
00:38:22,199 --> 00:38:22,959
for you too.

650
00:38:24,520 --> 00:38:25,239
Minglan.

651
00:38:27,320 --> 00:38:29,040
Sixth Miss,

652
00:38:29,040 --> 00:38:30,199
this match wasn't won easily.

653
00:38:30,360 --> 00:38:30,919
Come.

654
00:38:40,159 --> 00:38:41,679
Darling Second, you just lost like that?

655
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:44,199
You can't keep your champion title then.

656
00:38:46,280 --> 00:38:47,439
How does that matter?

657
00:38:48,439 --> 00:38:49,280
Why should I preserve it?

658
00:38:52,199 --> 00:38:53,439
The gold-silk pin.

659
00:38:56,159 --> 00:38:57,280
Thank you, Madam Wu.

660
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:58,760
You won this.

661
00:39:00,120 --> 00:39:01,719
Who does she think she is?

662
00:39:04,479 --> 00:39:05,120
Third Sister. Third Sister?

663
00:39:06,120 --> 00:39:08,399
Third Sister, it doesn't matter.

664
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:15,280
Hey! Have a seat now, Third Sister.

665
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:16,360
Don't be mad.

666
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:17,600
It's just a pin!

667
00:39:17,600 --> 00:39:19,000
We've got a jade bracelet.

668
00:39:25,159 --> 00:39:25,840
Third Sister!

669
00:39:32,120 --> 00:39:34,000
So amusing. Princess,

670
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:35,439
do you want to play polo?

671
00:39:37,080 --> 00:39:38,159
The ball is not interesting.

672
00:39:40,439 --> 00:39:41,439
The person is interesting.

673
00:39:44,800 --> 00:39:45,679
It was that Miss Sheng

674
00:39:45,679 --> 00:39:46,840
who went to battle in the match,

675
00:39:47,120 --> 00:39:49,080
but the award is to Miss Yu?

676
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:50,679
So did you lose

677
00:39:50,679 --> 00:39:51,800
to the Miss Sheng

678
00:39:52,120 --> 00:39:53,600
or Miss Yu?

679
00:39:54,679 --> 00:39:55,600
Look at how desperate

680
00:39:55,600 --> 00:39:56,439
Miss Sheng is.

681
00:39:57,280 --> 00:39:58,159
And Miss Yu cried

682
00:39:58,159 --> 00:39:59,479
many bouts

683
00:39:59,479 --> 00:40:00,600
for this pin.

684
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:03,199
Those two are of one mind.

685
00:40:03,800 --> 00:40:05,800
I merely wanted to make them happy.

686
00:40:07,840 --> 00:40:09,239
To add further,

687
00:40:09,239 --> 00:40:10,360
didn't you say

688
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:12,719
that Miss Yu is rarity?

689
00:40:13,639 --> 00:40:15,280
Gentle and virtuous?

690
00:40:17,239 --> 00:40:18,199
Yes.

691
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:19,919
Such a noble lady of

692
00:40:19,919 --> 00:40:21,080
gentle and virtuous nature.

693
00:40:22,040 --> 00:40:22,719
You can't find

694
00:40:22,719 --> 00:40:23,919
a second in the entire Bianjing City.

695
00:40:25,879 --> 00:40:27,120
She's such a good lady.

696
00:40:28,080 --> 00:40:29,280
Shouldn't let her be sad.

697
00:40:49,879 --> 00:40:51,399
Grandmother taught you polo.

698
00:40:51,719 --> 00:40:53,199
It was not to let you play with a man from outside.

699
00:40:57,919 --> 00:40:59,439
Third Brother ran away before the battle,

700
00:40:59,439 --> 00:41:00,560
and that's not what Grandmother taught us either.

701
00:41:04,159 --> 00:41:05,120
The Yu family has always

702
00:41:05,120 --> 00:41:06,399
gotten along well with Grandmother.

703
00:41:07,120 --> 00:41:08,800
My brother isn't

704
00:41:08,800 --> 00:41:10,320
as tyrannical as you

705
00:41:10,719 --> 00:41:12,280
to insist on knocking Yu Family's pride.

706
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:15,879
Eldest Miss Yu was raised

707
00:41:15,879 --> 00:41:17,719
by the Imperial Tutor since young.

708
00:41:18,239 --> 00:41:19,239
That's how they are close acquaintances

709
00:41:19,239 --> 00:41:19,800
with our grandmother.

710
00:41:20,479 --> 00:41:23,000
She agonized over her late mother's item,

711
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:24,520
and I felt empathy.

712
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:26,840
I think we are kindred souls in that way.

713
00:41:29,399 --> 00:41:30,679
It's really a coincidence then.

714
00:41:31,360 --> 00:41:33,239
You pitied the Eldest Miss of the Yu family,

715
00:41:33,800 --> 00:41:36,239
and Brother Yanruo pitied you too.

716
00:41:40,600 --> 00:41:41,520
The Young Lord of Qi House

717
00:41:41,520 --> 00:41:42,479
is man of upright disposition

718
00:41:42,479 --> 00:41:43,320
and loathes evil-doing.

719
00:41:44,760 --> 00:41:45,919
He saw that Third Brother

720
00:41:45,919 --> 00:41:47,280
ditched me all alone,

721
00:41:47,479 --> 00:41:48,360
so he extended help

722
00:41:48,360 --> 00:41:50,719
to me on Brother Changbai's account.

723
00:41:52,879 --> 00:41:53,560
Fourth Sister,

724
00:41:53,560 --> 00:41:55,159
not only did you not help me talk to Third Brother,

725
00:41:55,600 --> 00:41:56,719
you went and talked in depth

726
00:41:56,719 --> 00:41:57,560
with Sixth Young Master Liang.

727
00:41:58,479 --> 00:41:58,919
This is also not

728
00:41:58,919 --> 00:41:59,959
how a Fourth Sister should be either.

729
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:01,919
You!

730
00:42:10,199 --> 00:42:11,199
You're certain they will rest

731
00:42:11,199 --> 00:42:12,239
and feed the horses at Yuqing Monastery?

732
00:42:12,239 --> 00:42:13,760
I checked thoroughly.

733
00:42:13,760 --> 00:42:14,479
It's definitely so.

734
00:42:14,959 --> 00:42:16,239
Big Madam and Sixth Miss' maids

735
00:42:16,239 --> 00:42:17,080
were very tight-lipped.

736
00:42:17,479 --> 00:42:18,479
I thought I wouldn't

737
00:42:18,479 --> 00:42:19,520
be able to find out for you.

738
00:42:19,879 --> 00:42:21,439
But Miss Molan's maids

739
00:42:21,520 --> 00:42:22,600
told me first

740
00:42:22,600 --> 00:42:23,639
before I could even ask them.
